{"tid":656814,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"人死是否如燈滅","createTime":"2018-05-07T14:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T06:07:29.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc155984d73f56a6aa1e102aa47cbdc3072651e","tid":656814,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"bb3ea53e82d49a18d9a77ac8570a7130c8f7d307","tid":656814,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:12:54.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"b9e575ffca52615e03611dd47ad07a6a60b88603","tid":656814,"uid":34530,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"燈滅是否如人死?"},{"pid":"4786d67039a48f8159e2c0f0618665ae9e54245f","tid":656814,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"如果人唔係死如燈滅，其他生命體都唔應該係<br />\n你嘅精子都唔係<br />\n你死左要吞翻自己生前射過嘅全部精<br />\n因果有命；塵歸塵，士歸士，精歸口<br />\n喃嘸阿彌陀佛"},{"pid":"333e6788a9006ccd1cc9291f000fd0b950ae0dc0","tid":656814,"uid":111176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n人死左之後，咩都要放低<br />\n特別係果d自殺既人，得到解放同時都失去全部野，就好似好愛佢既屋企人、朋友<br />\n只要當你仲係生存緊，先有機會重來，邊個冇過去"},{"pid":"541aff79f32f20a7f8ff7f5eccf1b8221b91cb9a","tid":656814,"uid":67896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"最好係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想再有下世"},{"pid":"4f6ec5870da4fa7950e4ebce71ea182e2d1dbbd3","tid":656814,"uid":56713,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"如果巴打有留意開昂宿星人嘅話，應該會知道死亡只係我地靈魂要進入更高維度嘅其中一個體驗，所以死亡其實唔係終點，您嘅靈魂之後會再去其他嘅地方去學習同經歷"},{"pid":"7967600ec55fdea055824bfb1bde6499888a6ef4","tid":656814,"uid":44916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"燈熄咗可以再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75517e6785c8fe79f1fee29427a1278